creator: Bhotahiti
descriptionHtml:
This is business platform that provides both wholesale (bulk) buyers and sellers opportunity to buy and sell products at wholesale rate. it connects bulk buyers directly with the Factory , importers & wholesaler vice versa. this platform tends to resolve geographical challenges of buying and selling goods at business level by connecting business to the same platform through technology. This platform also provides solution the the problem small business by connecting them to the business related services. by ensuring direct connection to the bulk suppliers it cuts middle chain of supply thus increasing delivery hold time of goods thus increasing profitability of the buyers.

Single products buyers "single buyers" also can buy products as very discounted rates as products are directly from wholesaler and supplier rather then from retailers , unlike other ecommerce platform. Quality control. fastest delivery by catering limited number of supplier and buyers is key solution of the platform. providing loan to small businesses , providing inventory management feature directly through mobile application are other long term business related futuristic solutions.
descriptionShort: Bhotahiti | online wholesale is platform for wholesale buyers and sellers.

- Fastest Delivery
- Easy payment options
- Platform dedicated to Retail sellers
- Facility for small business loan
